title: DevFest The Netherlands
description:
The biggest Google tech conference in The Netherlands carefully crafted for you by GDG community, all about Android, Web and Cloud from the world experts!

See you on November 18th at Science Park 904 in Amsterdam!

aboutGdg: Google Developers Groups (GDGs) are open and volunteer communities of developers who share a passion for Google technologies.
teamPageText: Google Developers Group (GDG) The Dutch Android User Group is the main organizer of GDG DevFest The Netherlands. As an open and volunteer developer community who organize fun events around Google technologies, DevFest is just one part of the various eventsâ€”and they do it with loads of passion! The goal of DevFest NL is to organize a space to connect the best industry experts with Dutch developers and provide an opportunity for the like-minded to meet one another.
